quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,Aaron told them O my popol this est test vi. Your nur Lord est plej Gracious tial sekv me obe my ordon
  20,91,Ili dir Ni ad worship gxi Moses ven
  20,92,Moses dir O Aaron ki est gxi prevent vi when vi seg them ir astray
  20,93,El sekv my mend? Vi ribel me
  20,94,Li dir O fil my mother do ne tir me my barb my kap. Mi est afraid ke vi dir ‘Vi divid Infan Israel disobeyed my mend
  20,95,Li dir Ki est des materi vi O Samarian
  20,96,Li dir mi seg ki ili ne seg. Mi grabbed fistful (de polv) met kie messenger star uz gxi miks golden calf This est ki my mens inspir me do
  20,97,Li dir Tiam ir your life do ne eben ven close Vi hav appointed temp your final judgment vi neniam evade Jen your di vi uz worship ni brul gxi jxet gxi into mar al rest down tie forever
  20,98,Your nur di est DI; 1 beside whom tie ne est ali di. His knowledge encompasses all ajx
  20,99,Ni tiel narrate vi kelk news el generaci. Ni revealed vi message el us
  20,100,Those disregard gxi bor load (de pek) Tag Resurrection
  20,101,Eternally ili abide therein; ki miserable load Tag Resurrection
  20,102,Ke est tag when korn blov ni summon kulp ke tag blu
  20,103,(Flustr themselves ili dir Vi rest 1 life) ne plur than 10 tag
  20,104,Ni est fully aware da their utterances. Plej accurate among them dir Vi rest ne plur than tag